# {{projectName}}

DARE-shaped MCP server (TypeScript). Default transport: **{{defaultTransport}}**.

## Setup

```bash
cp .env.example .env
pnpm install
pnpm build
pnpm start
```

## Commands

- `pnpm dev` — tsx watch
- `pnpm build` — tsc to dist/
- `pnpm test` — vitest
- `pnpm lint` — ESLint
- `pnpm audit` — pnpm audit --audit-level=high
- `pnpm inspect` — MCP Inspector for the running server

